Package ca.ualberta.cmput301w14t08.geochan.json

Class Summary
BitmapJsonConverter Handles the serialization and deserialization of Bitmap objects to and from base64 JSON strings.
CommentJsonConverter Handles the serialization and deserialization of Comment objects to and from JSON format.
CommentOfflineJsonConverter Handles the offline serialization and deserialization of Comment objects to and from JSON format.
LocationJsonConverter Handles the serialization and deserialization of useful data in a Location to and from JSON format.
ThreadCommentJsonConverter Handles the serialization of a ThreadComment object into JSON format.
ThreadCommentOfflineJsonConverter Handles the serialization of a ThreadComment object into JSON format for offline caching.
